sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case TC_003_CSMS: Regular Charging Session - Plugin First
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6j - Chapter 3.2.1 (PDF pp. 110-111, Table 123)

    Note over CP: EV driver plugs in the cable

    CP->>CS: 1. StatusNotification.req

    CS-->>CP: 2. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: StatusNotification.req status MUST be "Preparing"

    Note over CP: EV driver presents identification

    CP->>CS: 3. Authorize.req

    CS-->>CP: 4. Authorize.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: Authorize.conf idTagInfo.status MUST be "Accepted"

    CP->>CS: 5. StartTransaction.req

    CS-->>CP: 6. StartTransaction.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: StartTransaction.conf idTagInfo.status MUST be "Accepted"

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req

    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf

    Note over CP,CS: Validation: StatusNotification.req status MUST be "Charging"
